&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Forward Deployed Engineer&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Remote&amp;nbsp; ·&amp;nbsp; Full Time&amp;nbsp; ·&amp;nbsp; Travel Required&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Insurance underwriting runs on human judgment, manual workflows, and knowledge locked in someone&#39;s head. It breaks when that person leaves and doesn&#39;t scale when the book doubles.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sixfold is building AI agents that understand risk the way a 20-year veteran underwriter does. We build systems that make real decisions on billions in premium for some of the world&#39;s largest carriers. AI is the product and the workflow.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Forward Deployed Engineer sits at the edge of what we&#39;ve built and what our customers need, making AI agents deliver in production. You&#39;ll be the senior technical partner on the ground with customers running joint architecture sessions, shipping integrations into their tech stack, and turning recurring patterns into platform capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a senior role for someone who lives and breathes AI tools. If your default workflow is Claude Code or Codex, you orchestrate parallel agents to ship feature work, enjoy spec driven development, and understand evals, tool use, and context engineering, then this role was created for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who We Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;🏔 Product: Sixfold is the AI brain for underwriting. Our platform handles submissions at scale, assessing risk against appetite, surfacing cited insights, and deploying AI agents to handle research, referrals, and triage so underwriters can focus on building profitable portfolios.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;💪 Team: A focused team of insurance operators, AI researchers, and engineers who love hard problems. We&#39;re pushing the boundaries of AI adoption across every function, from how we build, to how we sell and to how we support customers. We ship fast and stay close.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📈 Traction: Processing billions in premium for some of the world&#39;s largest carriers. We know AI. We know underwriting. We&#39;re building what comes next.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be Sixfold&#39;s first dedicated Forward Deployed Engineer, anchored to our newest product line and its customers. As we scale, you&#39;ll grow into the lead FDE role across Sixfold&#39;s product portfolio.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Own the technical relationship&lt;/strong&gt; with a portfolio of customers: joint architecture sessions, integration design, production debugging, and more.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Plug our product into each customer&#39;s ecosystem&lt;/strong&gt;: third-party data integrations, product customizations, and the deep integration work that embeds Sixfold in their underwriting stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ship the work yourself&lt;/strong&gt;, leveraging agentic engineering best practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Surface trends and patterns&lt;/strong&gt; from customer work and partner with product engineering to land them in the roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Translate fluently between audiences&lt;/strong&gt;: from &quot;what does this mean for our renewal&quot; with a Customer Success Manager, to &quot;what&#39;s the right primitive here&quot; with a product engineer, in the same afternoon.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Travel to customer sites&lt;/strong&gt; in the US when the work calls for it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Help shape the FDE function itself&lt;/strong&gt;: the operating model, the hiring bar, the success measures. You&#39;ll be a primary voice in what FDE at Sixfold becomes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
