&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Align engineering, product, and go-to-market teams.&lt;/strong&gt; Serve as the connective tissue between Engineering, Product, Customer Success, and Sales. Translate technical realities into language each team can act on. Make sure no important decision falls through the cracks and risks are owned/mitigated.&lt;/li&gt;
