&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Build lightweight, durable program infrastructure.&lt;/strong&gt; Design and own the minimum viable set of processes, tools, and tracking systems that keep programs running: roadmap and backlog planning, milestone tracking, dependency maps, risk registers, and executive dashboards. Processes should be owned and evolvable by teams, not dependent on you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Drive operational programs within Tech and across the company.&lt;/strong&gt; This could include managing the corporate and tech OKR processes, supporting 3-6 month planning horizons, continuing the org’s broader push toward agentic ways of working, etc. In general, staying plugged in and jumping in where you can add the most value.&lt;/li&gt;
